  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are actively selling into strength as SPX trades just below the massive 6830 gamma wall (+126B), with the recent wall break triggering hedging flows that likely contributed to the 5-min pullback despite strong 1-min momentum. The PIN regime with 479B total GEX creates a strong gravitational pull toward the 6825-6830 zone, where dealers will continue providing liquidity by selling rallies and buying any dips toward the 6777 flip level. Key inflection points are 6830 resistance (where dealer selling intensifies) and 6820 support (strong stabilizing level with +74B GEX).\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect price to get pinned between 6820-6830 with dealers capping upside moves.",
